{"tid":1906884,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"日本代購被人刪coupon，有冇辦法搵返個記錄","createTime":"2020-03-02T08:41:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-02T11:06:13.000Z","uid":168564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cba6b6f0002795226d1619bdeb61dafaa14aa70f","tid":1906884,"uid":168564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T08:41:46.000Z","msg":"早幾日見到之前用開個日本代購有張2442JPY運費 coupon，有啲心動琴日就搵佢哋代購。<br />\n<br />\n到咗今朝，見到張coupon已經比佢哋De咗。<br />\n明明到期日喺27.02-07.03<br />\n但佢哋嗰邊直接炸死，話完全冇呢張coupon存在。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E7z7c99.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE7z7c99.jpg&h=07427095&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家請問一下各位有冇辦法搵返個記錄出嚟？<br />\n我冇de Cookie同瀏覽記錄<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dTvFx9d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdTvFx9d.jpg&h=cfdb0311&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8d2b21ac655c4affb122c2f76e08cc0a199ec22d","tid":1906884,"uid":168564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T08:49:55.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"6c7525b73b6b6e29b2c0e9eff117991ccc3dd13a","tid":1906884,"uid":168564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T09:00:05.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"76ee1a444e89a0f039cc22d2da621edcd1575279","tid":1906884,"uid":168564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T09:14:23.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"7a60fff9a812ae9b74ffebb6c2fda234dcc50028","tid":1906884,"uid":168564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T11:06:13.000Z","msg":"自推"}]}